"12:22:6" : {s: 12, a: 22, w: 6, r: "علم", t: "وَعِلْمًۭا", l: "عِلْم", lc: 105, tl: "waʿil'man", lb: "জ্ঞান",e: "and knowledge", b: "ও জ্ঞান", i: "dan ilmu", f: 5, rm: "to mark/sign/distinguish, creations/beings, world, science/learning/knowledge/information, aware/know. By means of which one knows a thing, hence it signifies world or creation, because by it the Creator is known. alim (pl. ulama) - one who is learned/wise or knows."},
